Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.22,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,1075)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs80\c&H111111&\bord1\3c&d4c4d4&\blur2\b0}参谋大人 请喝茶
